  "combined_text": "--- Main Page ---\nVAS KOUZINA - Home\nVAS KOUZINA\nHome\nGIFT CARDS\nMenu\nSpecial Events and Catering\nGallery\nContact\n​​\nWelcome to our table\n​\nTrue Greek Cooking\nJoin us for Easter - Make your reservations Today\n​\nWine Down Wednesday\nwith\nHALF PRICE\nbottles of wine\nevery Wednesday\n​\nBROWSE MENU\nRESERVATIONS\n$15 LUNCH COMBO MENU\n$30 THREE COURSE MENU\nABOUT\nVasilios \"Billy\" Liakakos\n​Founded by Restaurateur Vasilios Liakakos whose passion has once again brought him back to his roots, with a desire to showcase true Greek cooking in a way it has never been done before. Having been in the dining industry in Georgia since 1995 he was inspired to bring a modern translation of authentic Greek fare to the Roswell and Alpharetta dining scene while transporting you to a favorite Greek village. With an affection for the foods he grew up on his dishes are infused with traditional flavors and techniques of classic Greek cuisine; prepared with fresh ingredients creating a style that is pure, light, and healthy. His expectations are to immerse you in a true Greek experience that goes beyond the amazing flavors of the food.\n​\nOur Dining Experience\nEnergetic and Inviting\nThe moment you step into our space you are exported to the true Greek experience\nfrom the people, the sounds, the atmosphere, and the amazing food.\n​We want to bring you into our world where we invite\n​you to sit at our table while you dine, share, and experience.\nBringing Pure Greek Food To The Table\nPURE  ~  LIGHT  ~  HEALTHY\nFOOD\n​meant to be shared\nCreate your own journey as you make your way through our Meze to our Ocean Apps, Spreads, and more. Completing your meal with a sweets course and selection of after dinner beverages.\n_______\nhighlights...\nWHOLE FISH\nSAGANAKI\nBAKED FETA\nMAROULOSALATA\nMELITZANOSALATA\nSAUTEED CALAMARI\nGRILLED OCTOPUS\n_______\nhighlights...\nGYRO\nSOUVLAKI\nSHRIMP SAGANAKI\nSQUID INK PASTA\n​GARDEN PLATE\nMENU\nDRINK to\nquench the\npalate\nOur Specialty\nFRESH PRESSED COCKTAILS\n​and INFUSION BAR\nCraft cocktails pressed with the freshest ingredients to engage all\nthe senses as you sip and enjoy\n​an infusion of flavors\n_______\nhighlights...\nGREEK 75\nCUCUMBER MINT SMASH\nGREEK MOJITO\nROSEMARY COLLINS\n_______\nhighlights...\nOUZO LEMON DROP\nCUCUMBER MARTINI\nMYKONOS MULE\nPEAR ELDERFLOWER SPRITZ\n_______\nhighlights...\nSparkling Infused Water\nWines imported from Greece\nMythos Hellenic Beer\nGreek Kafe\nFrappe\nFrappe Float\nDrink Menu\nRESERVE\nSKIP THE LINE\nRESERVE TABLE\nYou will be redirected to opentable.com to reserve table\nPlease call directly for parties of five or more so we can provide you the best accommodations\nCATERING\nWhole Restaurant Buy Out on Monday's\nIn need of that work lunch, board meeting, family gathering, or special event then look no further then our artfully designed establishment for all your needs.\nGet information\nDon't forget to check out our Fresh Market!\nRoswell\n942 Alpharetta St\n​Roswell, GA 30075\n678-587-5888\nRoswell Hours\nTuesday-Thursday 4pm-9pm\nFriday-Saturday 12pm-10pm\n​Sunday: 12pm - 8pm\nHome\nGIFT CARDS\nMenu\nSpecial Events and Catering\nGallery\nContact\n\n--- Page: /menu.html ---\nMenu - VAS KOUZINA\nVAS KOUZINA\nHome\nGIFT CARDS\nMenu\nSpecial Events and Catering\nGallery\nContact\nFROM THE KOUZINA\nCome   Gather   Share\nBAKLAVA\nTRUE GREEK\nDOLMADES\nMenu\n$30 THREE COURSE MENU\nLUNCH MENU\ndrink menu\nDessert Menu\nFAMILY MEALS TO GO\nCHEFS TABLE & WINE PAIRING DINNER EVENTS\nCUSTOMIZED DINNER WITH WINE PAIRINGS SERVED BY THE CHEF WITH ACCOMPANIMENT WINE POURED WITH EACH COURSE\nDon't forget to check out our Fresh Market!\nRoswell\n942 Alpharetta St\n​Roswell, GA 30075\n678-587-5888\nRoswell Hours\nTuesday-Thursday 4pm-9pm\nFriday-Saturday 12pm-10pm\n​Sunday: 12pm - 8pm\nHome\nGIFT CARDS\nMenu\nSpecial Events and Catering\nGallery\nContact\n\n--- Page: /uploads/1/1/8/1/118137039/vk_new_wine_cockail_menu_6.2023__1_